  m_text: "Be careful: a room can only hold up to 4 entities, so you need to plan
    out a good strategy to fend off the heroes efficiently. \r\n\r\nTo place entities
    in a room, click the room tile that you want to modify, and then click on the
    entity you want to add to the room. The entity will be automatically added to
    the selected room and will cost a certain amount of evil points."
