      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Every entity has a different price, and they also have different effects,
    so it's up to you to plan up your defences efficiently! \r\n\r\nAfter placing
    your desired number of entities, click \u201CConfirm\u201D to start the day,
    and the heroes will start flowing into your dungeons! "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
